## Migration Checklist

### D. Infrastructure
- [ ] Swap paths: `/opt/spark-data/` → `abfss://container@storage.dfs.core.windows.net/`
- [ ] Swap secrets: hardcoded Kafka keys → Databricks Secrets / Azure Key Vault
- [ ] Swap table naming: 2-level → 3-level Unity Catalog (`catalog.schema.table`)
- [ ] Remove manual SparkSession creation — wrap in `src/utils/spark.py`

### E. Orchestration
- [ ] Set up Databricks Workflows for batch SCD2 jobs
- [ ] Define job dependency chain: Landing → Bronze → Silver → Gold
- [ ] Configure retry policies (3 retries, 5-min delay)
- [ ] Configure failure alerts (Slack / PagerDuty)

### N. Security & Governance (Databricks-specific)
- [ ] PII masking on customer name, address, zip (Unity Catalog column-level masking)
- [ ] Access control: Analysts → Gold only, Engineers → all layers
- [ ] Enable Unity Catalog data lineage tracking (table-to-table dependencies)
- [ ] Tag PII columns with sensitivity labels in Unity Catalog

