## PII Columns to Mask (Unity Catalog)
These columns contain personally identifiable information and must be masked for analyst access:

| Table | Column | PII Type |
|---|---|---|
| `silver_enriched.customer_dim` | `first_name`, `last_name` | Name |
| `silver_enriched.customer_dim` | `city`, `zip` | Address |
| `gold_curated.dim_customer` | `first_name`, `last_name`, `city`, `zip` | Name + Address |

---

## What Does NOT Change
- Delta Lake format — fully supported in Databricks
- All Spark Structured Streaming logic — identical API
- DLQ pattern — same good/bad split, same `rejection_reason` column
- SCD2 MERGE logic — identical SQL
- Watermarking and window aggregations — identical API
- The 27-table medallion schema — no structural changes needed

