## Optional Table 28: `gold_delivery_status_RT`
If live BI joins on `delivery_fact_RT` + `delivery_partner_dim` prove too slow in Databricks SQL:
- Add a Stream-Static join in Spark: `readStream` on `silver_delivery_fact_RT`
- Join against latest `silver_delivery_partner_dim` (static read, refreshed each micro-batch)
- Group by `partner_name`, 5-min window
- `writeStream` to `gold_rt.gold_delivery_status_RT`

Decision gate: measure query latency in Databricks SQL first. Only build table 28 if latency > 5s.